Class JsonRowMap

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>

    public class JsonRowMap
extends java.util.AbstractMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
    Class representing a row of data as a map. This class parses JSON row data in the 8+ webservice API version format (ie. a simple array of values such as [1, "foo", null, true, 1.23]).
